metadata.name: Sunset Nightmare
metadata.description:
1/1
jpeg, 2000 x 2000

My first nightmare, I haven't seen long time ago but it's recurring in my eyes everyday , every moment .
This happens at sunrise but the sky was just like sunset but I don't think the sun came out on this day, really it was sunset, I don't know why he was thrown from above, I wish I could save him one day!

This painting is digitally drawn, and it is only one piece.
-Another world Seeker 
@cazoza
